OL,3,CClean air zone saves NHS #30,000 a
OL,4,Cmonth in first year
OL,6,FBradford's clean air zone has reduced
OL,7,Fair pollution and saved the NHS more
OL,8,Fthan #30,000 a month in its first
OL,9,Fyear, according to a study.
OL,11,FThe zone covers 22.4 square km, making
OL,12,Fit the second largest in England - and
OL,13,F20% of the city's population lives
OL,14,Finside it.
OL,16,FThe controversial low emission zone
OL,17,Fmeant that from September 2022, older
OL,18,Fand more polluting lorries, buses,
OL,19,Fcoaches and taxis have had to pay if
OL,20,Fthey drove in the zone. Private cars
OL,21,Fare exempt from the charge.
