OL,3,CClean air zone saves NHS #30,000 a
OL,4,Cmonth in first year
OL,6,FA new research project, Born in
OL,7,FBradford, has found in the first year
OL,8,Fof the scheme there were 700 fewer
OL,9,Fvisits to GP practices each month for
OL,10,Fheart or lung problems.
OL,12,FThe report found that's saved the NHS
OL,13,Faround #30,700 every month.
OL,15,FThe Government awarded #39m to
OL,16,FBradford Council to help implement the
OL,17,Fzone, and this money could be used to
OL,18,Fprovide grants to companies to upgrade
OL,19,FHGVs, taxis and buses.
