OL,3,CClean air zone saves NHS #30,000 a
OL,4,Cmonth in first year
OL,6,FBus operators were offered grants of
OL,7,Fup to #16,000 to convert the engines
OL,8,Fof buses to ones that would meet Clean
OL,9,FAir Zone emission standards. Many
OL,10,Fbuses in the city were retrofitted
OL,11,Fwith technology to reduce their
OL,12,Femissions.
OL,14,FHowever, a council meeting has now
OL,15,Fheard that the technology isn't
OL,16,Fworking and in fact buses are
OL,17,Fcontributing significantly to the city
OL,18,Fexceeding pollution limits in areas
OL,19,Fsuch as Manchester Road and Queen's
OL,20,FRoad.
